Title: Adapt commandline interface of agent controller
Class: fix
Compatible: incomp
Component: checks
Date: 1646248717
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0i1

This change only affects users who scripted the registration
command of the new agent controller <tt>cmk-agent-ctl register</tt>
using the first beta release.

The options of the command are now consistent with the options to
the similar updater command <tt>cmk-update-agent register</tt>.
